assessment_details.task_description:
For this assignment, you are required to work individually to complete Part 1, and in groups of five to complete Parts 2 to 4.

Your assignment questions and a detailed guide to this assignment are available on our course Blackboard site.

In brief, you will individually complete the Academic Integrity Tutorial (Part 1), while in your group, you will demonstrate:

your use and knowledge of correct terminology, mechanics and referencing in written work;

critical analysis of the literature;

evaluation of financing, with particular emphasis on crowdfunding versus traditional methods of entrepreneurial finance;

your understanding and analysis of capital budgeting techniques; and

peer assessment.

All parts of the assignment are to be submitted online.
